DemocracyMap,provides,a,simple,interface,that,helps,citizens,and,journalists,discover,the,civic,entities,and,governing,bodies,for,a,given,location,The,DemocracyMap,API,provides,contact,details,and,other,primary,information,on,all,governing,bodies,and,officials,representing,a,given,location,in,the,form,of,structured,data,A,demo,of,the,API,is,publicly,available,its,coverage,is,currently,limited,to,the,U,S